  m_Name: Times
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueNode
  npcName: Alty
  _npcRating: 0
  _isFinalNode: 0
  _lines:
  - It seems that's always been the case.
  - The people stopped to believe in us.
  - It's been decades since many of us have seen the sun.
  - Many of us can't conjure the strength to manifest beyond this point.
  - Well, execpt for Squimp...
  _playerReplyOptions:
  - Squimp?
  - I will make others believe.
